{"type": "article", "id": 25368, "title": "“纸片”烛台", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-13T07:14:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607110358oCc16kJPaNqhKLzS.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个黑色的方形“纸片”是一个烛台，是用金属做的。一个角离开桌面微微折起来以方便移动，它构成了微妙的深浅阴影对比，在视觉上给人一种轻盈的感受。一套 4 个烛台可以拼在一起或分开，构成有变化的图案。烛台中间有钉子插上蜡烛，可以适合不同型号。设计师来自西班牙，是为挪威品牌 Northern Lighting 而设计，<a href=\"https://northernlighting.no/news/drift-a-union-of-fire-and-ice/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110355sLE5efWc4O9mQnJq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110356CiATB1jyKYe6Ogox.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110357SvJYPcxdF10pa4DQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}